headline: Molina Healthcare Workforce Push Tests Margins And Long Term Valuation
summary: Molina Healthcare (NYSE:MOH) announced a workforce development initiative to train and hire 15,000 home health aides. The program spans 26 states and focuses on free, accessible training and career pathways in home based care. The company is targeting increased access to in home services and support for members who rely on long term and chronic care. The initiative arrives as healthcare providers adjust to sector challenges tied to government reimbursement rates. Molina Healthcare operates...
